  "body": "# Mob Info\n**This datapack allows you to see the name, health, and armor of the mob you are looking at.**\n\n![hud](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bfcc081588cc2e30fbadf2c07c5d3264e320d0c0.png)\n## Commands\n- **/function mob_info:toggle_armor**\n   > Hides the armor indicator.\n- **/function mob_info:toggle_hp**\n   > Hides the hp indicator.\n- **/function mob_info:toggle_name**\n   > Hides the name indicator.\n- **/function mob_info:toggle_style**\n   > Allows you to change the style.",
